import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { IPO } from 'src/app/models/ipo.model'; @Component({ selector: 'app-ipo', templateUrl: './ipo.component.html', styleUrls: ['./ipo.component.css'] }) export class IPOComponent implements OnInit{ list: IPO[]=[ { code: 'ABC', date: new Date('2023-05-01'), price: 10.0, quantity: 1000, }, { code: 'DEF', date: new Date('2023-05-02'), price: 12.0, quantity: 2000, }, { code: 'GHI', date: new Date('2023-05-03'), price: 8.0, quantity: 1500, }, ]; ngOnInit(): void { this.getList(); } getList() { throw new Error('Method not implemented.'); } apply(){ } }
